13753// getAltVSXFMAOpcode
13754LLVM_READONLY
13755int getAltVSXFMAOpcode(uint16_t Opcode) {
13756static const uint16_t getAltVSXFMAOpcodeTable[][2] = {
13757 { PPC::XSMADDADP, PPC::XSMADDMDP },
13758 { PPC::XSMADDASP, PPC::XSMADDMSP },
13759 { PPC::XSMSUBADP, PPC::XSMSUBMDP },
13760 { PPC::XSMSUBASP, PPC::XSMSUBMSP },
13761 { PPC::XSNMADDADP, PPC::XSNMADDMDP },
13762 { PPC::XSNMADDASP, PPC::XSNMADDMSP },
13763 { PPC::XSNMSUBADP, PPC::XSNMSUBMDP },
13764 { PPC::XSNMSUBASP, PPC::XSNMSUBMSP },
13765 { PPC::XVMADDADP, PPC::XVMADDMDP },
13766 { PPC::XVMADDASP, PPC::XVMADDMSP },
13767 { PPC::XVMSUBADP, PPC::XVMSUBMDP },
13768 { PPC::XVMSUBASP, PPC::XVMSUBMSP },
13769 { PPC::XVNMADDADP, PPC::XVNMADDMDP },
13770 { PPC::XVNMADDASP, PPC::XVNMADDMSP },
13771 { PPC::XVNMSUBADP, PPC::XVNMSUBMDP },
13772 { PPC::XVNMSUBASP, PPC::XVNMSUBMSP },
13773}; // End of getAltVSXFMAOpcodeTable
13774
13775 unsigned mid;
13776 unsigned start = 0;
13777 unsigned end = 16;
13778 while (start < end) {
13779 mid = start + (end - start) / 2;
13780 if (Opcode == getAltVSXFMAOpcodeTable[mid][0]) {
13781 break;
13782 }
13783 if (Opcode < getAltVSXFMAOpcodeTable[mid][0])
13784 end = mid;
13785 else
13786 start = mid + 1;
13787 }
13788 if (start == end)
13789 return -1; // Instruction doesn't exist in this table.
13790
13791 return getAltVSXFMAOpcodeTable[mid][1];
13792}

14184
14185 unsigned mid;
14186 unsigned start = 0;
14187 unsigned end = 180;
14188 while (start < end) {
14189 mid = start + (end - start) / 2;
14190 if (Opcode == getRecordFormOpcodeTable[mid][0]) {
14191 break;
14192 }
14193 if (Opcode < getRecordFormOpcodeTable[mid][0])
14194 end = mid;
14195 else
14196 start = mid + 1;
14197 }
14198 if (start == end)
14199 return -1; // Instruction doesn't exist in this table.
14200
14201 return getRecordFormOpcodeTable[mid][1];
14202}
